Dimensions of [Graphic LCD 84x48 - Nokia 5110](https://www.sparkfun.com/products/10168)

The overall size of the board is 45mm vertically and horizontally. For the screen, it’s about 40mm horizontal and 34mm vertical. The depth I measured from the top of the screen to the front of the board is about 3.75mm. If you measure the overall height, it’s about 5.1mm high from the top of the screen to the legs of the screen. For an image of these dimensions, try looking here 
